EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 15 JUN BY
   M/V BARBOROS HAYREDDIN PASA, M/V BRAVO SUPPORTER
   AND M/V DEEP SUPPORTER IN AREA BOUND BY
   35-31.6N 031-23.5E, 34-57.4N 031-49.4E,
   34-43.7N 031-22.4E, 35-17.8N 030-56.5E.
   SIX MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1148/14.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 16 JUN 14.
